,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b99421c6562d5c3b44ba30221e139b3fd7a69668","tid":564340,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"718420bf5f25a8cb4b738ee0d972ab6816c187bd","tid":564340,"uid":44690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁樓豬都係想睇下書啫<br />\n都係好事 唔好屌得咁恆<br />\n如果非圖書館扮工時間要睇書<br />\n可以去誠品打書釘 都開到好夜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"借書咪得囉<br />\n而加仲有網上預約送到去你屋企附近個間圖書館<br />\n一定要新年入去坐住睇先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6330f95a575c5caef5c59156650b44167c04309","tid":564340,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4676a650eddfa3209a0797a078fcb427042d56b0","tid":564340,"uid":79292,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bcc302bbbca5a2cb5cf49ee0cfbb3db4d3289a85","tid":564340,"uid":8308,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"其實圖書館可以24小時開放既，請個食Q睇場姐<br />\n如果個個都識自助借還書，交罰款，睇完書擺返原位已經解決左9成既問題<br />\n不過香港d圖書館係俾廢老打躉、賭鬼刨馬<br />\n根本唔係被人靜靜地睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"點解多廢老係因為佢嘅開放時間淨係得廢老得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過有次有個蝗女人同佢個蝗仔係圖書館玩捉依因<br />\n個保安望撚住兩隻蝗係度玩完全唔理<br />\n有個男人經過同佢講 呢度唔係遊樂場 要玩去公園玩<br />\n個蝗女人用唔咸唔淡嘅廣東話大叫 「關你撚事 我屌你老母」<br />\n個保安先同佢地講 「嘈到人喇」<br />\n如果開24擺個保安係度又真係有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5badeb507517514db96e96914071979898d99672","tid":564340,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"其實個app預約再拎書 幾好幾方便<br />\n自己住港島<br />\n中央館開既時間都好長<br />\n所以無問題"},{"pid":"d80fb1fc72ef51a46289e1eafeeff7944809fabc","tid":564340,"uid":12850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"6afc350ed0ca02f18a0dc26676fe289615f289bb","tid":564340,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58aa3679d15f4337443beede2a8b10f34fdbbfdf","tid":564340,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"學生+廢老+會睇書嘅人"},{"pid":"b0802434e17dd076482f40be4958995d856e8463","tid":564340,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bc90f2a87c01ae6384823965987dce5b4f5ba658","tid":564340,"uid":49974,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開朝七晚11 就差唔多 食工食完飯都可以入下去<br />\n<br />\n話晒d書我都有份比錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地唔洗收工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"即係咁 圖書館呢d公眾服務始終係server 市民大眾 若果 假日有咁既使用需求 開放又有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n至於你話洗唔洗收工 呢個係圖書館內部人手安排<br />\n你大家樂年初一都有人開工啦<br />\n<br />\n若果圖書館有合理既開放理由 其他人手等既問題都係小問題而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6320f2345bdbc7cb3914fd8c60a66a77eb492a","tid":564340,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d106cd19996952a361cd8196c58df387a2fa9bfd","tid":564340,"uid":62554,"like":8,"dislike":152,"score":-144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"中央收9點，唔好話我知你9點仲未收工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:36:0